HEADWORD: Quillback
<hw>Quill"back`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>An American fresh-water fish (<spn>Ictiobus cyprinus</spn> syn.
<spn>Carpiodes cyprinus</spn>); -- called also <altname>carp
sucker</altname>, <altname>sailfish</altname>,
<altname>spearfish</altname>, and <altname>skimback</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

